luxsimplelang (0.0.3) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Interface improvements:
    - Added splash screen with loading animation
    - Enhanced splash screen visibility
    - Set English as primary language
    - Improved window scaling and visibility
    - Added online manual link to documentation
  * Documentation updates:
    - Added comprehensive README.md
    - Updated user guide with new features
    - Added GitHub repository documentation
  * Performance improvements:
    - Optimized startup sequence
    - Enhanced application event handling
    - Improved theme switching performance

 -- Antonín Tomeček <bambiliarda@gmail.com>  Mon, 11 Sep 2025 15:00:00 +0200

luxsimplelang (0.0.2) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Enhanced GUI features:
    - Added line numbers
    - Adjustable font size
    - Improved syntax highlighting
    - Added status bar
    - Better theme contrast
    - Enhanced code editor
  * New language features:
    - File and directory operations (createdir, listdir, deletedir)
    - Text file operations (writefile, appendfile, readfile)
    - Text manipulation (upper, lower)
    - Alternative block ending with semicolon
    - Multiline comments /* ... */
    - Enhanced for loops with from..to syntax
  * Updated documentation and guide
  * Bug fixes and stability improvements

 -- Antonín Tomeček <bambiliarda@gmail.com>  Wed, 10 Sep 2025 14:30:00 +0200

luxsimplelang (0.0.1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release
  * Qt-based GUI implementation
  * Dark and light theme support
  * Czech and English localization
  * Syntax highlighting for LuxSimpleLang
  * File management (open, save, save as)
  * Built-in interpreter

